{{Infobox Journal | editor = Calvin L. Smith, Stephen Vantassel | frequency = annually | discipline = [[Theology]] | publisher = King's Evangelical Divinity School | history = 2012-present | country = [[United Kingdom]] | website = http://www.evangelicalreview.com | ISSN = 2053-6763 | abbreviation = Evangelical Rev. Theol. Politics }} The '''''Evangelical Review of Theology and Politics''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]], scholarly [[List of theological journals|theological journal]] published by the [[King's Evangelical Divinity School]], [[England]]. It is published annually with content being provided as available in electronic format delivered online. The journal defined its scope as "scholarly evangelical analysis of contemporary theological and political issues".{{citation needed|date=December 2017}}
