In [[Inuit mythology]], '''Tulugaak''' was the creator of [[light]]. The meaning of /tulugaq/ is 'raven';<ref>Lowenstein 1992, p. 214</ref> cf. the god [[Tuluŋigraq]] ("something like a raven"<ref>Lowenstein 1992, p. 10</ref>).

